{"tid":2302372,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"黎智英不滿遭抹黑控《大公報》誹謗 要求道歉兼賠償","createTime":"2020-11-27T05:25:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-27T07:19:40.000Z","uid":240362,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"19371ab2e05a78c0b2e6e96c9b91686ac706e802","tid":2302372,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T05:25:08.000Z","msg":"壹傳媒創辦人黎智英入稟高等法院，控告《大公報》今年6月發表題為〈亂港頭目謀「著草」 路線曝光 收費100萬〉的頭版文章，指內容屬惡意誹謗，抹黑指黎計劃非法潛逃離開香港、不遵守刑事案件保釋條件等。黎智英要求法院禁制《大公報》發佈同類內容，並下令其刊登道歉聲明，並作出賠償。<br />\n<br />\n兩名被告為大公報（香港）有限公司和註冊編輯賈西平。《大公報》今年6月25日發表涉案文章，原告黎智英7月3日發出律師信，要求《大公報》撤回文章、承諾不發佈同類誹謗內容、刊登道歉聲明及賠償合理金額，惟《大公報》拒絕所有要求。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201127/EVRF2N6S5VH5NNH4WFM2PHYAXQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201127%2FEVRF2N6S5VH5NNH4WFM2PHYAXQ%2F&d=jO1S1Ej7eDj8oQYGBWUFpBVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=b23fc093\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201127%2FEVRF2N6S5VH5NNH4WFM2PHYAXQ%2F&h=a17fd74a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201127/EVRF2N6S5VH5NNH4WFM2PHYAXQ/</a>"},{"pid":"d5e92ff47468c1f5fcf6e095497a5e365cf9010d","tid":2302372,"uid":160592,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T05:28:40.000Z","msg":"DONKI唔一齊告？"},{"pid":"9986bf04df495c2735350d0e3c9c8fdfe44fa527","tid":2302372,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T05:32:58.000Z","msg":"唔係坐緊監？"},{"pid":"25d84dafc1d085bbe6e3d2760b02833262758e48","tid":2302372,"uid":50101,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T05:34:54.000Z","msg":"告太公報=反支那=犯国安法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04ac1e73656a7d15d016d883047a08a05b0e19cf","tid":2302372,"uid":283021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T05:37:55.000Z","msg":"賈西.......平<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj